# ring-cors

Ring middleware for Cross-Origin Resource Sharing.

## Installation

Via Leiningen: [ring-cors "0.0.7-SNAPSHOT"]

## Usage

(def handler
  (-> routes
      (wrap-cors
       :access-control-allow-origin #\"http://example.com\"
       :access-control-allow-methods [:get :put :post :delete])))

